{"tid":462779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「13+3」藝術展　為良心犯打氣","createTime":"2017-11-09T01:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T03:20:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f101e4553f9c5ee6a81ef36c848e132922219b29","tid":462779,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:15:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171109/20208740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F20208740&d=iI%2B77h8RqrB2XqvfLFJKPB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=a6385cc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F20208740&h=f1006da5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171109/20208740</a><br />\n<br />\n「13+3」藝術展　為良心犯打氣<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171109/large/09la6p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171109%2Flarge%2F09la6p11.jpg&h=628e6a33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「13+3」展覽昨日開放，會場放有雨傘運動時抗爭者的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【聲援良心犯】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】東北案的13位囚友仍在牢獄中，重奪公民廣場案3人則獲准保釋上訴，為喚醒大眾對「13+3」良心犯的關注，有團體舉辦「13+3」藝術展，透過19位攝影師為「13+3」拍下的舊照，向公眾展現抗爭者的生活點滴，現場設一幅牆讓公眾貼上訊息，希望製造傘運連儂牆效果，稍後將訊息轉達獄中抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171109/large/09la6p12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171109%2Flarge%2F09la6p12.jpg&h=ec016dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n場內掛有一幅大型黃之鋒肖像。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171109/large/a0803a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171109%2Flarge%2Fa0803a.gif&h=d87eb293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邀公眾寫鼓勵語句<br />\n<br />\n展覽除上述攝影師在反東北等社會運動中拍下的攝影作品外，還有黃之鋒保釋出獄後照片，更邀請16位抗爭者家人提供照片，和撰文描述他們眼中的抗爭者。策展人黃定敏表示，籌備時間緊逼，由找場地到印製作品，只花了個半月時間。希望公眾除認識他們在鏡頭下抗爭的一面，還可認識生活中的他們。展覽亦邀請公眾把想對抗爭者說的話寫在告示貼，或把曾為抗爭者拍下的照片，都貼在展區牆上，希望藉此讓抗爭者知道「仲有好多人支持佢」。<br />\n<br />\n另一策展人阿龍表示，整理照片過程中喚醒許多回憶。例如他重看雨傘運動的照片，驚覺曾有這麼多市民到場支持，希望公眾不要忘記。<br />\n<br />\n攝影師之一的林健恆由反東北運動開始為抗爭者拍照，在傘運期間捕捉學聯周永康和岑敖暉在緊張局勢下難得展現的笑容，期望向公眾呈現抗爭者真實面貌。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李思潁"},{"pid":"25d19c866f79358414c8d82cc90fd2d7d2a5f184","tid":462779,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> push"},{"pid":"6698f43c965fef166d7ba44054dfcf9d3be92d52","tid":462779,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c3ce7097dbe6cd2de2256ebc570562977c251e","tid":462779,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"旺角義士呢？<br />\n<br />\n旺角義士就唔係香港良心？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f08ade3a0b0d201986b86010403ce21d89b9958","tid":462779,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:21:55.000Z","msg":"測風向先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58335bc910b02fc583145aea45e8c686a3c128fc","tid":462779,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:23:22.000Z","msg":"「抗爭者」藝術展就支持<br />\n只係13+3就不了"},{"pid":"2df0d804cda6d1b836712cd070cc834268cf30a7","tid":462779,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:24:54.000Z","msg":"全香港只有13+3先配叫做政治犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji